short_description.value:
Designed to mimic authentic, rustic timber planks, Baltimore is a fantastic way to bring the natural qualities of genuine wood into your home.

Key Features

  • Authentic replication of timber planks

  • Hardwearing porcelain construction

  • No need for post installation sealing

  • Available in four colour variants: Grey / White / Taupe / Beige

  • Produced using the latest inkjet technology

Due to the length of these tiles, slight curvature is to be expected. In order to compensate for this, we would suggest installing Baltimore in either a soldier (side by side) or staggered (1/4 bond) layout. 

Want eye-catching, wooden floors but don’t want the hassle of upkeep? The Baltimore range of wood effect tiles could be the answer to your dilemma. Constructed from durable porcelain and created using the very latest in HD inkjet printing technology, these aesthetically pleasing tiles look great in any setting. Astonishingly simple to install and even easier to look after, Baltimore comes in four colour variants, meaning that instilling a continuous rustic aesthetic in your interiors is an absolute cinch.
